<CONTENT id="_3549780_1"><TITLE value="Note to instructors"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;div align="center"&gt; 
 &lt;table style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-collapse: collapse; width: 795px; height: 174px;" border="1" cellpadding="15"&gt; 
  &lt;tbody&gt; 
   &lt;tr&gt; 
    &lt;td&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;**This part is not visible to students**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black;"&gt;Help with your Blackboard courses is available from&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;elearning@nmtafe.wa.edu.au&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"&gt;This&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; text-shadow: none !important; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-size: 13px; color: #000000; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"&gt;Introduction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;item (below)&lt;/span&gt;, should contain a welcome message and a description of the unit.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;Also in this area;&lt;/p&gt; 
     &lt;ul&gt; 
      &lt;li style="list-style-type: none;"&gt; 
       &lt;ul&gt; 
        &lt;li&gt;A link to your Learning and Assessment Plan (LAP)&lt;/li&gt; 
        &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;A link to a course evaluation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
       &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
     &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;You can then add your content within the &lt;strong&gt;Learning Materials&lt;/strong&gt; folder.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/td&gt; 
   &lt;/tr&gt; 
  &lt;/tbody&gt; 
 &lt;/table&gt; 
&lt;/div&gt; 
